template.name: Material Design Icons
template.description: Creates a new Material Design Icon drawable resource

parameter.name: DP
parameter.help: The icon size in device independent pixels

parameter.name: Resource Name
parameter.help: The name of the drawable resource to create

parameter.name: MDPI
parameter.help: If checked, a medium density drawable resource will be included

parameter.name: HDPI
parameter.help: If checked, a high density drawable resource will be included

parameter.name: XHDPI
parameter.help: If checked, an extra high density drawable resource will be included

parameter.name: XXHDPI
parameter.help: If checked, an extra extra high density drawable resource will be included

parameter.name: XXXHDPI
parameter.help: If checked, an extra extra extra high density drawable resource will be included
